{:benchmark/id :benchmark/sew-force-authorisation-custody-v1
 :benchmark/version 1
 :benchmark/status :experimental
 :benchmark/coverage-status :bounded
 :benchmark/domain :domain/protocol-value-conservation
 :benchmark/protocol :protocol/sew
 :benchmark/scenario-suite :suite/sew-force-authorisation-custody-v1
 :benchmark/scenario-suite-description
 "Force-authorisation grant, execution, expiry, replay, and held-custody scenarios.
